# Reference: https://docs.ansible.com/ansible/latest/playbook_guide/playbooks_variables.html#variable-precedence-where-should-i-put-a-variable
#
# The approach for now is:
#
# - group_vars/all - list all variables used in playbooks with default /
#      placholder values in groups_vars/all
# - group_vars/env/vars - non-sensitive, inventory specific variables
# - group_vars/env/secret - sensitive, inventory-specific variables. encrypted
#     using ansible-vault.
# - hosts - variables specific to ansible runtime (username, ports, etc)
